					<img itemprop="image" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/ImageObject" alt="Eva Longoria and Social Entrepreneurship" src="https://assets.entrepreneur.com/content/16x9/822/20160519193028-eva-longoria-2.jpeg" rel="share" />

